('Cuneyt', 'UK', 'Would like to start off by giving a big Thank you to Future Homes. A very reliable trustable estate agency company. The service they pride is top level & there communication level is amazing. They are very helpful & always there for you. Highly recommend with an A* Ali Bey the owner of Future Homes & his team Tolga & Bariş Thank you guys so much for everything & hope to deal with you again. You guys treated me like i was apart of a family member of yours than a customer!', 'https://futurehomesturkey.com/resize/1200/uploads/happy_customer/whatsapp-image-2024-09-05-at-16-33-11.jpg', '', ''),
